Dialogue: 99,0:00:03.65,0:00:05.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um grande desastre está por vir.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:07.03,0:00:10.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fada que jurou ser uma arauto da desgraça
Dialogue: 99,0:00:10.53,0:00:13.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arrastará as crescentes chamas brancas para uma situação severa.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Preste atenção.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:18.25,0:00:21.83,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É um banquete de tragédia.
